(2447,'FNTutorial','0000-00-00','NOTE SEBELUM MTC :\r\n1. Cek triggers\r\n2. Buka MySQLTool hapus sampah\r\n3. Putus sharingan d: induk di anak\r\n4. Rename Posrealtime exe\r\n5. innodb_force_recovery=16 ( Disarankan tambahkan my.ini pada saat dump backup)\r\n6. max_allowed_packet=256M ( Ketika restore error mysql has gone away tambahkan my.ini )\r\n7. mysqlcheck --auto-repair -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj --host=localhost --port=3306 pos -f\r\n8. Jika access denied, jalankan query di C:/Program Files/Indomaret/Mysql for pos.net/bin/\r\n\r\nRekomendasi S&D\r\n1. BACKUP QUERY\r\n\r\nCek dulu apakah di d:/ ada bekas backup dir *.sql dan hapus jika ada\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 --no-data pos -v > pos_struktur.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -usopp -p4gen1nd0m4ret -hlocalhost -P3306 --no-data soppagent -v > sopp_struktur.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 --no-create-info pos -v > pos_data.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -usopp -p4gen1nd0m4ret -hlocalhost -P3306 --no-create-info soppagent -v > sopp_data.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 pos prodmast -v > prodmast.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 pos serah -v > serah.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 pos vir_bacaprod -v > vir_bacaprod.sql\r\n\r\n2. Buka backup pos_struktur.sql dan sopp_struktur.sql dengan notepad, replace Ctrl+H find what utf8 ganti jadi latin1, Save. Buka My.ini innodb per tabel ubah jadi 1.\r\n\r\n3. MATIKAN SERVICES,MSC MYSQLFORPOSNET\r\n\r\n4. RENAME MYSQLDATAFILES !!!!\r\n\r\n5. KIRIM MYSQLDATAFILES BARU\r\n\r\n6. RESTORE QUERY\r\nmysql_upgrade -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata --force -hlocalhost\r\n\r\nmysql -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata -P3306 pos < pos_struktur.sql\r\n\r\nmysql -usopp -p4gen1nd0m4ret -hlocalhost -P3306 soppagent < sopp_struktur.sql\r\n\r\nmysql -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata -hlocalhost -P3306 pos -f < pos_data.sql\r\n\r\nmysql -usopp -p4gen1nd0m4ret -hlocalhost -P3306 soppagent -f < sopp_data.sql\r\n\r\nmysql -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata -hlocalhost -P3306 pos -f < prodmast.sql\r\n\r\nmysql -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata -P3306 pos -f < serah.sql\r\n\r\nmysql -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata -hlocalhost -P3306 pos -f < vir_bacaprod.sql\r\n\r\nmysql_upgrade -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata --force -hlocalhost\r\n\r\nmysqlcheck --auto-repair -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata --host=localhost --port=3306 pos -f\r\n\r\nganti mysql pass baru dan sinkron kan dengan dbl const.\r\n\r\n\r\nCara Tidak Rekomendasi Tapi Fast\r\nPOS BACKUP :\r\nmysqldump -uroot -p -hlocalhost -P3306 -v pos _his_wtran absen_kd alokasi_seasonal alokasi_seasonal_temp atk_config atk_cons atk_ktgplastik atk_log atk_masterplastik atk_mstran atk_pbatk atk_prodmast atk_rumus atk_stmast avg_sls bank barcode batas batelurcatcod bayar bcx_temp beritaacara beritaacara_penukaran beritaacara_penukarandetil bincard bln_akt bracket bracket2 bracket_temp brx_fbx_main_temp brx_fbx_tdkmain_temp brx_fbx_temp brx_temp buah cancel ccard closing_detail const const_asm custmast custom danakas dcmast dcp_boxplu del_temp dept dhx_temp disc_istore disc_istore_harian diversity_tbldetailnc diversity_tblhapusnc diversity_tbllayanan diversity_tbllogharga diversity_tblnc diversity_tbloption diversity_tblsj diversity_tblttb diversity_tblversi divisi edcmas elpiji emailnrb expired_main expired_main_old fbx_main_temp fbx_temp fee filterplu fixed_tb fixed_tb_new fixtabel fstruk grmast hadiah hasil_his_pb hbx_temp his_retur_roti his_spd nominal_kas ft_all_toko his_stock his_switching his_tk his_tkn hisptagnr hitung_his_pb hrgbeli hrgbeli_new hrn_rak hsprodmast icard_config icard_fee icard_jeniskartu checklist checklist_setting toko_checklist toko_kunjungan toko_unit dc_npbtoko_log dc_npbtoko_file icard_member icard_pushmember icard_tipetransaksi icard_trans idelivery_callcenter ide