(446,'FNTutorial','NOTE SEBELUM MTC :\r\n1. Cek triggers\r\n2. Buka MySQLTool hapus sampah\r\n3. Putus sharingan d: induk di anak\r\n4. Rename Posrealtime exe\r\n5. innodb_force_recovery=16 ( Disarankan tambahkan my.ini pada saat dump backup)\r\n6. max_allowed_packet=256M ( Ketika restore error mysql has gone away tambahkan my.ini )\r\n7. mysqlcheck --auto-repair -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj --host=localhost --port=3306 pos -f\r\n8. Jika access denied, jalankan query di C:/Program Files/Indomaret/Mysql for pos.net/bin/\r\n\r\nRekomendasi S&D\r\n1. BACKUP QUERY\r\n\r\nCek dulu apakah di d:/ ada bekas backup dir *.sql dan hapus jika ada\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 --no-data pos -v > pos_struktur.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -usopp -p4gen1nd0m4ret -hlocalhost -P3306 --no-data soppagent -v > sopp_struktur.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 --no-create-info pos -v > pos_data.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -usopp -p4gen1nd0m4ret -hlocalhost -P3306 --no-create-info soppagent -v > sopp_data.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 pos prodmast -v > prodmast.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 pos serah -v > serah.sql\r\n\r\nmysqldump -uroot -pfH+cu2vIZa3QD+UCfrWUL1fKhBsEFgCzM=PsoRr0pMwj -hlocalhost -P3306 pos vir_bacaprod -v > vir_bacaprod.sql\r\n\r\n2. Buka backup pos_struktur.sql dan sopp_struktur.sql dengan notepad, replace Ctrl+H find what utf8 ganti jadi latin1, Save. Buka My.ini innodb per tabel ubah jadi 1.\r\n\r\n3. MATIKAN SERVICES,MSC MYSQLFORPOSNET\r\n\r\n4. RENAME MYSQLDATAFILES !!!!\r\n\r\n5. KIRIM MYSQLDATAFILES BARU\r\n\r\n6. RESTORE QUERY\r\nmysql_upgrade -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata --force -hlocalhost\r\n\r\nmysql -uroot -p$d3@pr15mata -P3306 pos < pos_struktur.sql\r\n\r\nmysql -usopp -p4gen1nd0m4ret -hlocalhost -P3306 soppagent